EXIT.TO.CALLING.PROGRAM: *************************************************
* exit the method entirely.  pops return stack until a return is         *
* done to the calling subroutine.  this subroutine allows exit.method    *
* and exit.sub to cleanly exit a subroutine or method even from inside   *
* a subroutine called with a gosub                                       *
